label: about_section
text: AstroMirror is a free astrology and calendar software. All features work without internet.Display panchang including calculation related to tithi nakshatra vaar karan and yoga. It also calculates the table of ascendant of any day.Display information like running tithi sunrise in calendar format for easy view and also display festivals.Display kundli for the given detail also calculate vimshottri dasha upto prandasha and yogini dasha up to antardasha it also displays the varshphal.Gives facility of ashtkoot milaan.Display information like different muhurth running throughout the day hora and chaughadiya of any day.The developer has worked to the best of his abilities to develop this software. If you think there is any inconsistency in the information displayed or you want to give some feedback. Send email at feedbackdtw@gmail.com.Your feedback and suggestions are welcomePrivacy PolicyAstroMirror uses Google Analytics to track the behavior of how this application is being used. To track some information is collected like OS version what feature of the app being used. No personal information is collected. All such information is collected for the development purposes and for the betterment of this app. About
